g.text: by clicking on the User,, the page will be readdressed
to the User profile, where the event manager
Here how the front end interact with the Algorithm:
- the event manager can call the algorithm to create the groups
- the algorithm answer with a pool of possible groups
- the event manager choose with which group(s) continue
by clicking on the green mark
- the event manager must check the groups
-the event manager can confirm the group
- the new group will be stored and the users notified
- by calling ERASE GROUPS, the event manager erase the groups
can be there a mixed combination of groups: for 5 ppl, 4,3 or 2 ppl.
based on the score and the availability of the host/location
by closing the event, the manager declare that the event has been
executed and no more action can be done on it.
before to close the event, remember the manager to collect the feedback!
by publishing the event, the manager declare that the event
is ready and can be showed to the users.
from now, users can express their interest
an automatic message will be sent to the user to remember them
to write the feedback in the rating section
by CONFIRM the event, the manager declare that the user have been choosed
And the event is ready to be executed
